# --- Agent files tracked on main (synced from orchestration-tools) ---
# These are Ruler-generated but intentionally tracked on main.
# The Ruler section above ignores them, but these !exceptions override
# so they remain tracked. Must come AFTER the Ruler section (last match wins).
